5:
What's that? You want to go back to
Palpebra?
13: Of course! But... Are you sure?
17:
That assassin is no doubt still
prowling the streets of Palpebra
looking for you.
22:
...I know, but... I can't keep running
away forever.
25:
So I've decided to try and talk to
him...
29:
...He's not here? Last time he came
right away... I wonder if the location
is the problem?
32:
Maybe? But if things got out of hand
like last time, a town wouldn't be the
best option...
36:
Hm. Maybe he just gave up? That
sure does save us the hassle.
40:
Unlikely. A man like that wouldn't
give up so easily.
52:
I don't want to be an assassin... I'm
just an adventurer!
55:
...Pure nonsense. Today is the day
that I open your eyes to the truth.
62:
Enough talk. Your talents lie
elsewhere.
65:
...No matter how hard I try, it seems
like you'll never listen to what I have
to say...
73: Yes... I will settle this... by myself!
90:
He brought backup, huh? Shoulda
seen that coming.
102:
Finally... You've decided to get
serious?
106:
Because you were going to hurt
Stella!
109:
If that's what it will take, then I'll
make you put that knife to work!
114:
Show me what you're REALLY
capable of! Otherwise, your friends
are done for.
117:
S-stop! They have nothing to do
with this!
120:
Yes! That's what I'm talking about!
Show me that BLOODLUST!
121:
Society will never accept you! You're
an outsider... a servant of the
shadows, like me!
127:
But even if that is the case, I will
never become someone like you.
130:
Because I'm an adventurer! That's
what my friends see me as, and
that's what I'll always be!
133:
Such abilities are entirely wasted on
you!
136:
There's nothing I could ever learn
from you!
140:
So don't EVER come near me or my
friends, ever again.
146:
Heh, that was quite the show you
put on back there. The look of
disappointment on that assassin's
face was priceless!
150:
In any event, that should settle
things. You'll now be able to walk the
streets of Palpebra in peace, Vivi.
155: You were great out there, Vivi.
160:
Thank you... But now that I think
about it, some good did come out of
this experience...
162:
It was scary, but in the end I was
able to meet all of you...
165:
And I gained a little more
confidence along the way! Like this!
Watch!
172:
I can even sneak up behind Nimbus
without him noticing!
